    <div class="ublpmb-faq__inner">
      <span class="ublpmb-eyebrow">— FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="ublpmb-h2">Common <em>questions.</em></h2>
      <details class="ublpmb-faq__item">
        <summary>Will UBurn treat my menopause symptoms?<span class="ublpmb-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublpmb-faq__body">No — and no honest brand should claim that. UBurn is a dietary supplement that supports <strong>satiety</strong>. The glucomannan (konjac plant fiber) forms a gel in your stomach for up to 4 hours of fullness, which helps with the hormonal sugar cravings that intensify in your 40s and 50s. It does not treat, prevent or cure menopause.*</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublpmb-faq__item">
        <summary>How is this different from a "menopause" supplement?<span class="ublpmb-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublpmb-faq__body">Most menopause stacks pack 10-14 actives at low doses. UBurn does one thing: a clinically dosed glucomannan-based satiety drink, EFSA-recognized for the satiety claim within a calorie-controlled diet. Caffeine-free, 30 calories, plant-based.*</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublpmb-faq__item">
        <summary>I'm on HRT / metformin / Ozempic — is it safe?<span class="ublpmb-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublpmb-faq__body">UBurn is a food-based dietary supplement (plant fiber + minor actives, no hormones, no stimulants). Glucomannan can affect the absorption of oral medications — always take it at least 1 hour before or after any prescription. Ask your doctor if you have specific concerns.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublpmb-faq__item">
        <summary>When will I notice a difference?<span class="ublpmb-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublpmb-faq__body">Satiety: from the first scoop. The afternoon sugar craving usually feels noticeably softer within 7-14 days of daily use. Effects on weight are individual and depend on overall calories and movement.*</div>
      </details>
      <details class="ublpmb-faq__item">
        <summary>Subscribe or one-time?<span class="ublpmb-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="ublpmb-faq__body">Both. Subscribe &amp; save gives −10% + free bonuses (e-book, Collective, WhatsApp coach, free U.S. shipping). Pause, skip or cancel anytime from your account. No lock-in.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
